# <type>: <summary> (50 chars max)
#
# Types:
#   feat     - new skill, trigger phrase, workflow, or script
#   fix      - corrects a bug or broken behavior
#   docs     - adds or updates a handoff, guide, or reference doc
#   chore    - maintenance (cleanup, renaming, reorganizing)
#   refactor - restructures existing content without changing behavior
#
# Body (optional — wrap at 72 chars):
# - What changed and why
# - Key files affected
# - Session handoff: handoffs/<filename>.md (if applicable)
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add verbatim-analysis skill and trigger phrase
#   docs: add Workspace_Guide_2026-06-26 handoff
#   chore: move trigger phrases ref doc from skills/ to docs/
#
# Lines starting with # are ignored by git.
